<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>Verifikasi Email</title>
    <script src="https://www.gstatic.com/firebasejs/6.2.0/firebase-app.js"></script>
    <script src="https://www.gstatic.com/firebasejs/6.2.0/firebase-auth.js"></script>
    <script src="https://www.gstatic.com/firebasejs/6.2.0/firebase-firestore.js"></script>
   
    <style>
        body {
            background: url('./image/bg-home.png') no-repeat;
            background-size:cover;
        }
        
        .verif-box {
            max-width: 25rem;
            text-align: left;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body class="h-full">
    <div class="nav fixed-top">
        <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark m-auto w-100 fixed-top bg-purple">
            <div class="container">
                <a class="navbar-brand text-light" href="/">Kiddos</a>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </div>
    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center h-full">
        <div class="p-5 text-center bg-white box">
            <h3><strong>Verifikasi Email Anda</strong></h3>
            <div class="py-4 verif-box">
                <p>Hi <strong id="name"></strong>! Silakan cek email Anda untuk melanjutkan verifikasi email Anda. Klik tombol dibawah jika email belum diterima.</p>
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-between ">
                    <input type="button" value="Kirim Ulang" class="btn button btn-link text-decoration-none mt-3" id="kirimVerifikasi">
                    <input type="button" value="Keluar" class="btn button btn-link mt-3 text-decoration-none" id="signout">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script src="./js/jquery.js"></script>
    <script src="./css/bootstrap-4.4.1-dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    <script src="./js/verificationEmail.js" type="module" defer></script>
</body>

</html>